          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How versatile are Summer Kurtas for different occasions?",
            "text": "<p>Summer Kurtas are among the most adaptable pieces in any ethnic wardrobe. Whether you're heading to a brunch, office meeting, festive gathering, or vacation, our Summer Kurta Sets offer effortless elegance. Pair them with denim for a casual vibe, or wear with palazzos and statement earrings for a semi-formal or festive look. Their lightweight fabric and breathable silhouettes make them ideal for both day and evening wear during warmer months.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_HgTM6p": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What makes our Pastel Kurta Sets unique?",
            "text": "<p>Our Pastel Kurta Sets are crafted using soft, breathable fabrics like cotton and cotton-silk blends, ensuring maximum comfort in warm weather. What truly sets them apart is the thoughtfully curated pastel palette‚Äîthink soothing blush pinks, mint greens, sky blues, and buttery yellows. These tones not only keep you cool but also add a modern, refreshing touch to traditional ethnic wear. Each design blends minimal embroidery or print detailing with timeless cuts, making them both elegant and wearable.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_rNJDpL": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Can these Summer Kurtas be styled for both casual and formal events?",
            "text": "<p>Absolutely. Our comfortable pastel ethnic wear is designed with versatility in mind. For casual outings, pair your pastel kurta with straight pants and Kolhapuris. To elevate it for formal events, opt for co-ord kurta sets with dupattas, accessorize with jhumkas and metallic flats, and add light makeup. These styles transition seamlessly from a laid-back day look to a refined evening ensemble.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_yhzFrk": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "How do pastel colors enhance summer ethnic wear?",
            "text": "<p>Pastel shades are ideal for Indian summers‚Äîthey reflect heat, feel calming to the eye, and exude understated elegance. Our pastel kurta sets are inspired by nature‚Äôs summer palette and handpicked to flatter all skin tones. Beyond aesthetics, pastels blend beautifully with traditional motifs and contemporary cuts, making them a favorite for women seeking comfortable pastel ethnic wear with a fresh and youthful vibe.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_zJMNt7": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What occasions are best suited for wearing Summer Kurta Sets?",
            "text": "<p>Our Summer Kurta Sets are versatile enough for a wide range of occasions:<br/>Workwear: Go for clean-cut, solid pastel kurtas with minimal prints<br/>Festive Events: Choose sets with subtle embroidery or block prints, paired with a light dupatta<br/><br/><br/>Travel or Brunch: Opt for breezy cotton kurtas styled with juttis and a tote<br/><br/><br/>Home Entertaining: Choose relaxed fits in soft hues, accessorized with handcrafted jewellery<br/> The beauty of this collection lies in how effortlessly it transitions across moods and settings.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_fYYEwy": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Are these Summer Kurtas comfortable for all-day wear?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, comfort is central to our design philosophy. These Summer Kurtas are made from breathable, lightweight fabrics that allow easy movement and airflow, making them perfect for all-day wear‚Äîeven in peak summer heat. Our relaxed fits and thoughtful tailoring ensure that you feel just as good as you look throughout the day.</p>"
