            "text": "<p>Styling pastel kurtas is all about balance. For a minimalist daytime look, pair with nude sandals, dainty studs, and a natural makeup palette. To dress it up, opt for oxidized silver jewelry, bold bangles, and embellished flats. Bags in earthy tones or soft pastels add a cohesive finish. You can even layer your Summer Kurta with a cropped jacket or dupatta for more formal flair.</p>"
